00:51:44.000 --> 00:51:45.800
That was the first year
we had ever done it.

00:51:45.800 --> 00:51:47.290
I had got it the second
year, but the first year,

00:51:47.290 --> 00:51:48.590
I was just a finalist.

00:51:48.590 --> 00:51:49.890
I didn't get it.

00:51:49.890 --> 00:51:51.190
I was very upset.

00:51:51.190 --> 00:51:52.810
I wanted to quit because
I didn't have a drive.

00:51:52.810 --> 00:51:54.110
I was , I don't know."

00:51:54.110 --> 00:51:59.720
But at the end of the day,
