00:52:15.010 --> 00:52:18.060
And I just can't --

00:52:18.060 --> 00:52:21.380
me personally, I just
can't explain anything

00:52:21.380 --> 00:52:23.280
like that other than God.

00:52:23.280 --> 00:52:26.150
Like I just can't;
like there's no way.

00:52:26.150 --> 00:52:30.510
There's no way that that wasn't
something that He put in my life

00:52:30.510 --> 00:52:32.750
to tell me to keep going.

00:52:32.750 --> 00:52:35.030
So I mean, He's the
reason why I do it,

00:52:35.030 --> 00:52:36.690
and that is the reason
why I love Him.

00:52:36.690 --> 00:52:37.990
