talking earlier about how it's

00:54:30.130 --> 00:54:32.900
so important to have youth,

00:54:32.900 --> 00:54:34.600
people who are traditionally
excluded

00:54:34.600 --> 00:54:37.780
from the national narrative
in this type of setting.

00:54:37.780 --> 00:54:44.050
But I was -- I asked myself,
"What is the point of being here

00:54:44.050 --> 00:54:46.970
