here and fully present,

00:54:46.970 --> 00:54:50.680
if I have to leave parts of my
identity outside of the room?"

00:54:50.680 --> 00:54:55.070
So I thought that was so
important to me, and especially

00:54:55.070 --> 00:54:57.750
with the poem "Why We March".

00:54:57.750 --> 00:55:00.830
I mean, obviously, I'm
really passionate about it.

00:55:00.830 --> 00:55:04.120
And I thought especially
given this platform,

00:55:04.120 --> 00:55:09.610
and given the location, it is
something that I have to say.

00:55:09.610 --> 00:55:13.500
And in terms of my
process; so I'm super busy,

00:55:13.500 --> 00:55:15.380
after this I'm going
to take a train home,

00:55:15.380 --> 00:55:16.870
I'm going to get
home at like 1:40,

00:55:16.870 --> 00:55:18.830
and I have to go
to school tomorrow.

00:55:18.830 --> 00:55:23.490
