convoluted way helps my poetry,

00:55:28.340 --> 00:55:32.150
because when I do write, I know
that I'm going to have two,

00:55:32.150 --> 00:55:34.820
three hours and I have
to say what I want to say

00:55:34.820 --> 00:55:36.270
in those two, three hours.

00:55:36.270 --> 00:55:39.810
So when I sit down and write,
I'm not fooling around,

00:55:39.810 --> 00:55:42.990
I write what I think is true,
I write what I want to say,

00:55:42.990 --> 00:55:44.520
and I write what I
think it's important

00:55:44.520 --> 00:55:46.250
for other people to hear.

00:55:46.250 --> 00:55:50.250
Because I think my voice, and
all the voices of the people

00:55:50.250 --> 00:55:54.310
on this stage are so
important, especially right now.

00:55:54.310 --> 00:55:57.640
And so when we write, it's
