01:17:57.790 --> 01:18:00.120
I am passionate.

01:18:00.120 --> 01:18:02.070
I am a global citizen.

01:18:02.070 --> 01:18:04.610
I speak for places
I'm connected to.

01:18:04.610 --> 01:18:09.060
I have to say what I want
to say, what I need to say.

01:18:09.060 --> 01:18:17.450
We have a messa, we
foster community,

01:18:17.450 --> 01:18:20.330
we empower the voices of others.

01:18:20.330 --> 01:18:24.230
You are showing up, showing
out, and showing us."

01:18:24.230 --> 01:18:26.030
Thank you.

